item.title: SoftLayer_Account_Authentication_Attribute
item.description: SoftLayer_Account_Authentication_Attribute Service Datatype Description Account authentication has many different settings that can be set. This class allows the customer or employee to set these settigns. Local accountId The internal identifier of the SoftLayer customer account that is assigned an account authenction attribute. Type: integer id A SoftLayer account authenction attribute's internal identifier. Type: integer typeId The internal identifier of the type of attribute that a SoftLayer account authenction attribute belongs to.
